---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../config/site';
const updated = 'July 5, 2026';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use"
  description={`Terms of Use for ${site.name}, an educational initiative of ${site.company}. Please read these terms before using the website.`}
>
  <section class="container legal-wrap">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last Updated: {updated}</p>

    <p class="legal-lead">Welcome to <strong>{site.name}</strong>. These Terms of Use constitute a legally binding agreement made between you, whether personally or on behalf of an entity ("you"), and <strong>{site.company}</strong> ("we," "us," or "our"), concerning your access to and use of the {site.name} website.</p>

    <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
    <p>By accessing or using the website, you signify that you have read, understood, and agreed to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with these terms, you are expressly prohibited from using the site and must discontinue use immediately.</p>

    <h2>2. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
    <p>Unless otherwise indicated, the website is our proprietary property. All source code, databases, functionality, software, website designs, audio, video, text, photographs, and graphics on the website (collectively, the "Content") and the trademarks, service marks, and logos contained therein are owned or controlled by <strong>{site.company}</strong> and are protected by copyright and trademark laws.</p>

    <h2>3. User Representations</h2>
    <p>By using the website, you represent and warrant that:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You have the legal capacity and you agree to comply with these Terms of Use.</li>
      <li>You will not access the website through automated or non-human means, such as bots, scripts, or scrapers.</li>
      <li>You will not use the website for any illegal or unauthorized purpose.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Prohibited Activities</h2>
    <p>You may not access or use the website for any purpose other than that for which we make the website available. Prohibited activities include, but are not limited to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Attempting to bypass or modify the security features of the website.</li>
      <li>Copying or adapting the website's software (including our simulators and calculators) or any part thereof.</li>
      <li>Systematically retrieving data or other content from the website to create or compile a collection, compilation, database, or directory without written permission from {site.company}.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>The website is provided on an "as-is" and "as-available" basis. You agree that your use of the website and our services will be at your sole risk. <strong>{site.company}</strong> makes no warranties or representations about the accuracy or completeness of the website's content or the content of any websites linked to this website.</p>

    <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>In no event will <strong>{site.company}</strong>, its founder (Louis F.), or its contributors be liable to you or any third party for any direct, indirect, consequential, exemplary, incidental, special, or punitive damages, including lost profit, lost revenue, loss of data, or other damages arising from your use of the website.</p>

    <h2>7. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms shall be governed by and defined following the laws of the State of New York. <strong>{site.company}</strong> and yourself irrevocably consent that the courts of New York shall have exclusive jurisdiction to resolve any dispute which may arise in connection with these terms.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right, in our sole discretion, to make changes or modifications to these Terms of Use at any time and for any reason. We will alert you about any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date of these Terms of Use.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For any questions or comments regarding these Terms of Use, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><strong>{site.company}</strong><br />Attn: Privacy Department<br />PO Box 17223<br />Rochester, NY 14617<br />Email: {site.contactEmail}</p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-wrap { max-width: 720px; padding: 56px 32px; }
  .legal-wrap h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .legal-updated { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .legal-lead { padding: 18px 20px; border: 1px solid var(--bg-4); border-left: 3px solid var(--blue); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--bg-1); color: var(--text); font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .legal-wrap h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 28px 0 10px; }
  .legal-wrap p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal-wrap ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin: 6px 0 14px; }
  .legal-wrap li { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.65; padding-left: 16px; border-left: 2px solid var(--line); }
  .legal-wrap strong { color: var(--text); }
</style>
